Package: bjscrapeR
Type: Package
Title: An API Wrapper for the Bureau of Justice Statistics (BJS)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dylan", "McDowell", email = "dylan.mcdowell226@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Drawing heavy influence from library(blscrapeR), this library is meant to be a tidy wrapper around the Bureau of Justice Statistics (BJS) API. The idea is to utilize the 'tidyverse' methodology to create an efficient workflow when dealing with crime statistics.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
  readr,
  dplyr,
  glue,
  rlang
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dylanjm/bjscrapeR
BugReports: https://github.com/dylanjm/bjscrapeR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
